<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Marcus Aurelius @if(visible) Quotes @end</h2>
    <p>You have power over your mind - not outside events. Realize this, and you will find strength.</p>
</body>
</html>